D, meet some Ukranien defence companies. One of the military supplier company interested our products.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:black;\\\">Now SAGA is in contact with this company and they are negotiating for 1.000.000 sgm UHMWPE fabric and 100.000 pcs NIJ Level IV ceramic plates. Regarding this order they have some questions below.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">- Tests are carried out at a distance of -10 meters</span></em></strong><strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1F497D;background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">- Ballistic barrel (SVD; СВД)</span><span style=\\\"background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">- Cartridge 7,62x54R with bullet B-32; V- 830 + - 15 m/s</span><span style=\\\"background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">The bulletproof vest is attached to the installation with a unit of ballistic clay; on each plate installed in the vest should be made three shots; between hits and the edges of the plates should be at least 50 mm. In addition to the results for no penetration, a depth of beyond barrier injury should be checked on fingerprints on clay (not less than 25 mm).</span><span style=\\\"color:#1F497D;background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">Features of the bullet B-32:</span><span style=\\\"background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">type - FMJ (steel capsule coated with tompack - 90% cuprum and 10% zinc); weight - 10.4g; length - 38,15 mm; ballistic coefficient - 3,01 sq.m/kg; the mass of the core - 5,48 g; core material - steel Y12; length of core - 28,5 mm; diameter of core - 6,14 mm; kinetic energy ~ 3700 J.</span><span style=\\\"background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">According to its data, this bullet is almost similar to M2A</span></em></strong><strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1F497D;background-color:yellow;\\\">P</span></em></strong><strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">, except that there are two incendiary compositions - the head and bottom.</span><span style=\\\"color:#1F497D;background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">In addition, following his instructions, I forward some questions to you:</span><span style=\\\"color:#1F497D;background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">we are interested in cooperation with your company in the context of acquisition from your company the following:</span><span style=\\\"color:#1F497D;background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">&nbsp;- Fabric UHMWPE. Please send to our address the physical and mechanical characteristics of the fabric and indicate its width, weight of 1 sq.m, breaking characteristics, and cost.</span><span style=\\\"color:#1F497D;background-color:yellow;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1A1A1A;background-color:yellow;\\\">- Ceramic plates. Please specify which content of the ceramic plate, the size of the ceramic plates, specify the thickness of the ceramic according to the IV class of protection of NIJ standard. And if possible please send to our address the certificate of quality on ceramics. The cost of the plate.</span></em></strong><strong><em><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\"></span></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:black;\\\">We urgently need the technichal data package of the customers questions. It is a very serious Project and their top management will visit SAGA very soon.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:black;\\\">Waiting your earliest convenience.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:black;\\\">Best Regards,</span> \r\n</p>',1439273293,'1439273436',0,1439274142,1439378257,0,0),(103,389,389,1,'任务主办','',0,'test','<div style=\\\"color:#333333;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:5px 5px 5px 0px;font-family:arial;font-size:12px;\\\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>From:</strong><span class=\\\"Apple-converted-space\\\">&nbsp;</span>\\\"Kadir Nisasta &lt;kadir.nisasta@sagasavunma.com.tr&gt;\\\"\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>To:</strong><span class=\\\"Apple-converted-space\\\">&nbsp;</span>\\\"\\\'\\\'陈寅捷\\\' \\\' &lt;chenyinjie@siruichina.com&gt;\\\"\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>CC:</strong><span class=\\\"Apple-converted-space\\\">&nbsp;</span>\\\"xinzhirong &lt;xinzhirong@siruichina.com&gt;\\\"\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>Sent:</strong><span class=\\\"Apple-converted-space\\\">&nbsp;</span>2015-08-10 23:32\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>Subject:</strong><span class=\\\"Apple-converted-space\\\">&nbsp;</span>UKRANIAN PROJECT -!-\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\\\"color:#333333;font-family:verdana, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;\\\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<div class=\\\"WordSection1\\\">\r\n			<div>\r\n				<div>\r\n					<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n						<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:black;\\\">Dear Sonnie,</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">\r\n						<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:black;\\\">Last month you know we visited Ukranine and their MOD, meet some Ukranien defence companies. One of the m